  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/bc489b59e13be6cbb3e86a45f06dc3c0.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=614 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/bc489b59e13be6cbb3e86a45f06dc3c0.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/bc489b59e13be6cbb3e86a45f06dc3c0.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i>You draw, I guess</i> is a delightful and engaging drawing game that offers six modes to show your artistic talents and imagination! Immerse yourself in the world of creativity and connect with players all around the world!<br><br>6 Game Modes<br><strong>1. Real-time Guess:</strong> 2-10 players required. 1 player draw and the others guess on the word. The one who first answers correctly can score.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/3a8953ef47ebc65cd4b328ebcd98ea4b.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/3a8953ef47ebc65cd4b328ebcd98ea4b.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/3a8953ef47ebc65cd4b328ebcd98ea4b.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2. Classic Mode:</strong> Draw pictures or guess on drawings in an offline mode. Pass your pictures or guessing words to the next players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f03279f3539d71949f18e98ce3103658.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f03279f3539d71949f18e98ce3103658.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f03279f3539d71949f18e98ce3103658.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3. Drawing Master:</strong> Start your immersive drawing experience in an unlimited time. Enjoy the pleasure of art creation!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/d54ab71dbd1319d8aa504a136f2816de.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/d54ab71dbd1319d8aa504a136f2816de.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/d54ab71dbd1319d8aa504a136f2816de.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4. Collobration in Story Telling:</strong> Collorate with other players, use your imagination to complete a story with 10 drawings in total.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/21b51f1bc4de9f4c9e0840ede2db468e.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/21b51f1bc4de9f4c9e0840ede2db468e.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/21b51f1bc4de9f4c9e0840ede2db468e.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>5. Make the Drawings Dance:</strong> Let the static paintings animate and experience the charm of animation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f37fafe68864dc81f574c2a95c0319fe.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f37fafe68864dc81f574c2a95c0319fe.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/f37fafe68864dc81f574c2a95c0319fe.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>6. Creative Doodles:</strong> Draw on the colored patterns and create interesting doodles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/64582c497d804c4a0d4b918aabe0781a.poster.avif?t=1737937942\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/64582c497d804c4a0d4b918aabe0781a.webm?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2688400/extras/64582c497d804c4a0d4b918aabe0781a.mp4?t=1737937942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Whether you're a seasoned artist or a novice doodler, <i>You draw, I guess</i> offers you a diverse and inclusive space for you to express yourself through art and storytelling.",
